=== Fork Modifications ===

The following modifications were made to the original CubeSandbox in this fork
("Cube Container"):

1. Added mcp-server-go/ — a Go MCP (Model Context Protocol) server exposing
   161 container orchestration tools for AI agents, covering Docker
   orchestration, hypervisor management (KVM/libvirt VM lifecycle, ZFS
   storage, GPU passthrough, cloud-init), RBAC with argon2id, rate limiting,
   AES-256-GCM secrets management, and a tamper-evident audit hash chain.

2. Added deploy/container-mode/ — Docker, Caddy (TLS+WAF+rate limit), and
   one-click deployment configuration for container-mode operation.

3. Added web/ — a React/Vite/Tailwind dashboard for cluster management.

4. Added skills/ — operational runbooks for human and AI operators.

5. Modified Cubelet and CubeMaster for container-mode (non-MicroVM) operation
   with overlayfs storage and runc runtime.

6. Added hypervisor layer — 32 tools for VM lifecycle (libvirt), ZFS storage
   management, GPU passthrough (NVIDIA VFIO), and cloud-init provisioning,
   with input validation across all attack surfaces (7 security audit rounds,
   56 findings resolved).

